## Screen Details

### 1. Home Screen
The main chat interface.
*   **Main Area**:
    *   **Guest Banner**: Warning for guest users (local storage only).
    *   **Welcome Screen** (Empty State):
        *   **Greeting**: "Hi [Name] ðŸ‘‹".
        *   **Hero Question**: "What can I help you with?".
        *   **Suggestion Pills (Mobile)**: Quick prompts (e.g., "Make a website", "Color Palette").
    *   **Message Feed**: Container for User and AI chat bubbles.
*   **Input Area (Bottom/Fixed)**:
    *   **Inline Suggestions**: Popups appearing when text is typed (e.g., "Create a stunning portfolio...").
    *   **File Upload Input**: Hidden file input.
    *   **Textarea**: "Ask LYNQ anything..." placeholder.
    *   **Toolbar**:
        *   **Left Group**:
            *   **Attach Button (+)**: Dropdown for **Camera**, **Photos** (Gallery), **Files**.
            *   **Tools Button**: Dropdown for **Canvas**, **Web Search**, **Create Image**, **Deep Research**, **Shopping**, **Thinking**.
            *   **Selected Tool Indicator**: Shows active tool icon and name with a deselect (X) button.
        *   **Right Group**:
            *   **Model Selector**: Dropdown to choose specific model (e.g., llama-3.1).
            *   **Voice Button**: Microphone icon.
            *   **Send Button**: Up arrow (changes to Stop button during generation).
    *   **Footer Text**: "LYNQ AI can make mistakes..." and Developer credit.
*   **Canvas Pane (Right Split-View)**:
    *   **Header**:
        *   **Tabs**: Code / Preview.
        *   **Formatting Toolbar**: Bold, Italic, Heading, List (for document editing).
        *   **Actions**: Download Code, Close Canvas.
    *   **Content**:
        *   **Monaco Editor**: Code editor view.
        *   **Preview**: Iframe for rendering HTML/CSS.

### 2. Login / Sign Up Screen
Split-screen layout (on Desktop).
*   **Left Panel (Form)**:
    *   **Header**: Logo, Title ("Welcome back!" / "Create Account"), Subtitle.
    *   **Social Login**: Buttons for **Google**, **GitHub**, **Phone**.
    *   **Divider**: "Or".
    *   **Email Form**:
        *   Name Input (Sign Up only).
        *   Email Input.
        *   Password Input.
    *   **Phone Form** (Toggled): Phone Number input, Verification Code input.
    *   **Action Button**: "Sign in with email" / "Create Account".
    *   **Toggle Link**: Switch between Login and Signup.
    *   **Footer Links**: Help, Terms, Privacy.
*   **Right Panel (Image)**:
    *   **Background Image**: Scenic visuals.
    *   **Overlay Content**:
        *   **Title**: "Get Started with Us".
        *   **Steps**: Visual indicators for 1. Sign up, 2. Workspace, 3. Profile.

### 3. Profile Screen
*   **Hero Section**:
    *   **Large Avatar**: Image or Initial with "Change" camera button.
    *   **Name & Email**.
    *   **Plan Badge**: e.g., "Free Plan".
*   **Account Information Card**:
    *   **Email Address**.
    *   **Phone Number**.
    *   **Member Since** date.
*   **Quick Actions**:
    *   **Change Avatar**: Opens Avatar Picker.
    *   **Settings**: Link to the Settings screen.
    *   **Help Center**: Link to the Help screen.
    *   **Logout** (Danger style).
*   **Guest View**: Alternative card prompting login if user is not authenticated.

### 4. Projects Screen
*   **Header**:
    *   Title: "My Workspace".
    *   Subtitle: "Your generated apps, scripts, and history."
*   **Grid Layout**:
    *   **Project Cards**:
        *   **Icon**: Specific to type (Python, React, etc.).
        *   **Badge**: Status (Generating, Completed, Draft).
        *   **Title**: e.g., "Data Scraper Script".
        *   **Description**: Short summary.
        *   **Action Arrow**: "View Code" / "Resume Editing".

### 5. Tools Screen
*   **Hero**:
    *   Title: "AI Tools".
    *   Search Bar: "Search tools..." input.
*   **Category Filter Pills**: All, Coding, Research, Content, Data.
*   **Tool Sections** (Grouped by category):
    *   **Development Suite**: Canvas, Regex Builder, API Tester.
    *   **Research & Data**: Web Search, Data Analysis, Web Scraper, SQL Generator.
    *   **Creative Studio**: Writing Assistant, Resume Builder, Email Templates.
*   **Tool Card Content**:
    *   Icon & Badge (Popular, New, Live).
    *   Title & Description.
    *   **Suggestion Chips**: Quick prompts to launch the tool (e.g., "Landing page", "AI news").

### 6. Settings Screen
*   **Header**: "Settings".
*   **Personalization Group**:
    *   **Theme Toggle**: Light/Dark mode switch.
    *   **Accent Color**: Color picker circles (Gold, Green, Blue, Red).
*   **Intelligence Group**:
    *   **Custom Instructions**: Textarea to set system persona/rules.
*   **Developer Settings Group**:
    *   **BYOK**: Inputs for OpenAI Key and Gemini Key (Saved locally).
*   **Data & Privacy Group**:
    *   **Export Data**: Download JSON Button.
    *   **Clear All History**: Danger button to wipe local/server data.
*   **Support Group**: Links to the Help Screen and "About LYNQ AI".

### 7. Help Screen
*   **Header**: "Help Center" with "Back to Settings" button.
*   **Search Bar**: "Search for articles...".
*   **Quick Access Cards**: Getting Started, Billing & Plans, Community.
*   **FAQ Section**: Accordion items (e.g., "What is LYNQ AI Pro?", "Is my data private?").
*   **Contact Support Form**:
    *   Status Indicator ("All Systems Operational").
    *   Inputs: Name, Email (auto-filled), Subject, Message.
    *   "Send Message" button.
